    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Sliding Mechanics</strong></h2>Experience the thrill of sliding at exhilarating speeds on ice, mastering skillful movement and agility to conquer each challenge with precision and control.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/82a35e1e8e4593762d3051ac11305f3e.poster.avif?t=1729526975\" width=480 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/82a35e1e8e4593762d3051ac11305f3e.webm?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/82a35e1e8e4593762d3051ac11305f3e.mp4?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Time Trials and Ghost Races</strong></h2>Compete against your own best times and others, with ghost data automatically linked to leaderboard entries. Download and challenge top players' ghosts to refine your techniques.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/51952d78e0c1b55769cefbb92e333786.poster.avif?t=1729526975\" width=480 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/51952d78e0c1b55769cefbb92e333786.webm?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/51952d78e0c1b55769cefbb92e333786.mp4?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging Levels</strong></h2>Conquer meticulously designed courses, dodging enemies with speed and skill on your quest for victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/daded86d83f5d6a2dc91f1d43e78e049.poster.avif?t=1729526975\" width=480 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/daded86d83f5d6a2dc91f1d43e78e049.webm?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/daded86d83f5d6a2dc91f1d43e78e049.mp4?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Power-Ups</strong></h2>Discover various power-ups that boost your speed, agility, and abilities, strategically using them to gain an edge during races.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/850c2eb96c6e64b3dea35d6d377d0eb1.poster.avif?t=1729526975\" width=480 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/850c2eb96c6e64b3dea35d6d377d0eb1.webm?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/850c2eb96c6e64b3dea35d6d377d0eb1.mp4?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Global Asynchronous Multiplayer</strong></h2>Race against friends and players worldwide, competing against their ghost data in seamless multiplayer races.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/947fa08541d642446f68bd425976a0a3.poster.avif?t=1729526975\" width=480 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/947fa08541d642446f68bd425976a0a3.webm?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006420/extras/947fa08541d642446f68bd425976a0a3.mp4?t=1729526975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Competitive Leaderboards</strong></h2>Aim for the fastest times and climb the global leaderboards. Compare your performance with friends and top players to determine who truly reigns supreme on the ice.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Progression and Ranks</strong></h2>Improve your time trial scores to ascend the overall leaderboard ranks and achieve new levels of mastery!",
